WEBVTT

00:00:33.310 --> 00:00:35.270
CHETYRNADTSATOGO APRELYA,

00:00:35.270 --> 00:00:37.148
TYSYACHA DEVYAT'SOT

00:00:37.148 --> 00:00:39.384
DEVYANOSTO SHESTOGO GODA.

00:00:39.928 --> 00:00:41.584
INTERV'YUIRUYEMYY:

00:00:42.073 --> 00:00:44.496
BELLA LANDMAN.

00:00:44.704 --> 00:00:47.712
NASTOYASHCHAYA FAMILIYA: RABINOVICH.

00:00:47.848 --> 00:00:49.760
INTERV'YUIRUYUSHCHIY:

00:00:50.192 --> 00:00:51.984
XAIM BARGMAN.

00:00:52.528 --> 00:00:54.360
GOROD: KAUNAS.

00:00:54.512 --> 00:00:56.464
STRANA: LITVA.

00:00:56.761 --> 00:00:58.720
YAZYK: IDISH.

00:01:05.279 --> 00:01:07.407
haynt iz der fertseter april,

00:01:07.543 --> 00:01:10.726
fun toyznt nayn hundert zeks un nayntsikstn yor.

00:01:10.726 --> 00:01:12.231
mir gefinen zikh

00:01:12.760 --> 00:01:14.135
in Lite,

00:01:14.583 --> 00:01:15.743
in Kovne.

00:01:16.040 --> 00:01:17.735
dem intervyu vet gebn

00:01:18.055 --> 00:01:19.911
Beyle Rabinovitsh,

00:01:20.072 --> 00:01:21.999
fun der heym, Landman.

00:01:22.599 --> 00:01:24.583
dem intervyu vet nemen

00:01:24.895 --> 00:01:26.879
Khaim Bargman.

00:01:32.943 --> 00:01:40.999
ikh bin geborn gevorn in toyznt nayn hundert tsvey, in oktyaber, toyznt nayn hundert tsvey un tsvantsikstn yor.

00:01:40.999 --> 00:01:44.450
ikh hob gelebt in Yaneve.

00:01:44.442 --> 00:01:46.344
vu iz dos, Yaneve?

00:01:46.351 --> 00:01:49.563
Yaneve, hinter Kovne, draysik kilometer.

00:01:49.563 --> 00:01:55.245
dernokh hob ikh gelebt in Yaneve, un fun Yaneve bin ikh aribergeforn in Kovne vu ikh hob gelebt.

00:01:54.549 --> 00:01:56.549
ir gedenkt ayer lebn in Yaneve?

00:01:56.549 --> 00:01:58.715
ikh gedenk, a bi- a bisl gedenk ikh.

00:01:58.478 --> 00:02:01.622
dertseylt a bisele, vos gedenkt ir vegn dem lebn in Yaneve?

00:02:00.140 --> 00:02:04.830
nu vos, nu vos s'iz ge- geven aza lebn vi, vi umetum.

00:02:04.830 --> 00:02:07.915
 vos, mit vos hobn zikh farnumen ayere eltern?

00:02:07.915 --> 00:02:11.873
mayne eltern hob ikh dokh aykh gezogt; der foter iz geven a toker.

00:02:11.873 --> 00:02:14.112
nor dernokh iz er krank gevorn

00:02:14.112 --> 00:02:16.943
un er hot ke- shoyn nit gearbet bay di arbet

00:02:16.943 --> 00:02:19.746
un mir gehat a krom mit a bekeray.

00:02:19.746 --> 00:02:21.422
un ver hot gearbet in di bekeray?

00:02:21.422 --> 00:02:22.971
der foter mit di muter.

00:02:22.971 --> 00:02:25.970
vos flegt ton der foter in bekeray? vos flegt ton di muter?

00:02:25.970 --> 00:02:30.717
nu, (nu), me, zey flegn azoy makhn di di, nu, vi in a bekeray.

00:02:30.717 --> 00:02:34.886
ikh fleg oykh an andersh mol helfn dortn, bashmirn, ba-

00:02:34.886 --> 00:02:39.363
 oysmakhn, un dernokh bin ikh aribergeforn in Kovne lebn.

00:02:38.573 --> 00:02:41.868
vart a bisele. umgefer dertseylt merer

00:02:41.868 --> 00:02:43.753
vegn, vegn Yaneve.

00:02:43.753 --> 00:02:47.294
vos iz, vos, ir, az ir flegt helfn

00:02:47.294 --> 00:02:49.990
bashmirn, dos flegt ir ton in ovnt, bay nakht, in

00:02:49.655 --> 00:02:52.507
in mitn nakht fleg ikh oyfshteyn fir a zeyger.

00:02:52.507 --> 00:02:55.200
un ir flegt geyn in bekeray, ah, helfn ayere eltern.

00:02:54.950 --> 00:02:56.292
f- helfn mayne eltern.

00:02:56.163 --> 00:02:58.999
un, mit vos hot gehandlt di krom?

00:02:58.999 --> 00:03:03.114
nu, v- alts iz geven. mel un tsuker; vos ir vilt.

00:03:03.114 --> 00:03:05.835
bay aykh, bay aykh iz geven a groyse mishpokhe?

00:03:05.835 --> 00:03:08.655
bay undz iz ge- mir zaynen geven

00:03:08.655 --> 00:03:12.015
zi- fir kinder, zeks man

00:03:12.015 --> 00:03:13.523
mit di eltern.

00:03:13.523 --> 00:03:16.179
ir zayt, nokh der rey velkhe zayt ir?

00:03:16.179 --> 00:03:17.638
ikh bin di tsveyte.

00:03:17.638 --> 00:03:19.213
un der ershter iz ver geven?

00:03:19.015 --> 00:03:19.949
a bruder.

00:03:19.949 --> 00:03:21.081
vi iz geven zayn nomen?

00:03:20.966 --> 00:03:21.999
Shloyme.

00:03:21.999 --> 00:03:24.730
ir zay- ir zayt di, ir zayt di tsveyte in der mishpokhe.

00:03:24.163 --> 00:03:25.425
ye.

00:03:25.425 --> 00:03:29.232
nakher iz geven nokh a bruder, un nakher iz geven a shvester.

00:03:28.638 --> 00:03:30.737
iz zog zeyere nemen bite.

00:03:30.737 --> 00:03:32.245
Shloyme

00:03:32.245 --> 00:03:36.278
nu, mayne iz Beyle, m'hot, iz dos Fayvl-Leyzer

00:03:36.278 --> 00:03:37.606
un Khaye-Sore.

00:03:37.606 --> 00:03:39.097
Khaye-Sore iz geven di yingste.

00:03:39.097 --> 00:03:39.835
ye.

00:03:39.835 --> 00:03:40.819
der mizinikl.

00:03:40.819 --> 00:03:41.786
ye.

00:03:41.786 --> 00:03:44.163
 zogt mir, in

00:03:44.163 --> 00:03:46.524
in der shule, hot ir ongehoybn geyn in Yaneve?

00:03:46.524 --> 00:03:47.458
in Yaneve.

00:03:47.458 --> 00:03:48.802
vos iz dos geven far a shul?

00:03:48.802 --> 00:03:51.769
in Yavne hob ikh gelernt, a folkshul.

00:03:51.769 --> 00:03:52.819
a folkshul.

00:03:52.819 --> 00:03:55.917
m'hot gelernt litvish, hebreish,

00:03:55.917 --> 00:03:57.360
yidish.

00:03:57.360 --> 00:04:00.524
vifl yor hot ir zikh opgelernt in di folkshul Yavne?

00:03:59.294 --> 00:04:02.285
nu, fir, fir, klasn hob ikh geendikt.

00:04:01.884 --> 00:04:02.745
fir klasn?

00:04:02.671 --> 00:04:03.073
ye.

00:04:02.983 --> 00:04:05.491
di lere in Yavne, oyf vosere shprakh iz gegangen?

00:04:05.491 --> 00:04:08.410
oyf, iz gegangen a shprakh oyf hebreish, flegt men rey-

00:04:07.819 --> 00:04:08.917
altsding oyf hebreish?

00:04:08.917 --> 00:04:11.158
merer teyl flegt men reydn oyf hebreish.

00:04:10.867 --> 00:04:13.441
lemoshl, aykh hot men gelernt rekhenen,

00:04:13.441 --> 00:04:14.654
matematike?

00:04:14.589 --> 00:04:17.392
matematike oykh oyf hebreish, alts.

00:04:17.392 --> 00:04:20.163
ober ikh gedenk shoyn nit. ikh gedenk shoyn nit.

00:04:20.048 --> 00:04:23.168
un ah yidish hot men aykh oykhet gelernt? s'iz geven a limed yid-?

00:04:22.359 --> 00:04:26.999
neyn, yidish hot men nit gelernt. yidish iz geven spetsyel a folkshul oyf yidish.

00:04:26.999 --> 00:04:28.392
ober ir zayt dort nisht gegangen.

00:04:28.392 --> 00:04:30.982
neyn, ikh hob zikh yidish oysgelernt aleyn.

00:04:30.982 --> 00:04:33.146
 di eltern hobn geredt yidish?

00:04:33.146 --> 00:04:36.343
ye, un shraybn hob ikh zikh oysgelernt aleyn vayle

00:04:36.343 --> 00:04:41.656
tsu di hebreishe AZBUKA tsu di yidishe, di zel- zelbike.

00:04:38.753 --> 00:04:41.458
yidisher alefbeys iz der zelbiker.

00:04:41.458 --> 00:04:46.688
un de- un der, ir gedenkt dem yor ven ir zayt aribergeforn in Kovne?

00:04:46.688 --> 00:04:48.343
ikh gedenk nit.

00:04:48.343 --> 00:04:51.327
ober ir, ir, dos iz shoyn geven nokh der folkshul.

00:04:51.327 --> 00:04:53.409
nokh der folkshul, ye.

00:04:53.409 --> 00:04:56.016
nu, ikh bin shoyn geven mistomen a yor

00:04:56.016 --> 00:04:59.032
a yor zekhtsn, zibetsn mistomen.

00:04:59.032 --> 00:05:03.178
oyse- vos hot ir geton nokh dem vi ir hot geendikt di folkshul in Yaneve?

00:05:02.983 --> 00:05:07.034
keyn zakh hob ikh nit geton; kh'hob gelebt bay mayn onkl, se hot mir keyn zakh nit gefelt

00:05:07.034 --> 00:05:08.835
mayn onkl iz geven zeyer a raykher.

00:05:08.835 --> 00:05:09.836
vu, in Kovne?

00:05:09.836 --> 00:05:12.770
ye. Landmans, fun di mebl-gesheftn.

00:05:12.770 --> 00:05:17.666
iz, dertseylt a bisl merer vegn ayer onkl, dos iz geven der mame's bruder tsu der tatn?

00:05:16.868 --> 00:05:23.294
d- dem tatn's bruder; dos iz geven, nu, Hirshl Landman, der vos iz geshtorbn in, vos iz geshtorbn do.

00:05:23.294 --> 00:05:28.704
zey zaynen geven aroysgeshikt in Rusland; dernokh zaynen zey gekumen tsurik in Kovne.

00:05:28.704 --> 00:05:33.016
nu, un ikh bin dernokh ave-, undz hot men dernokh avekgefirt in kovner geto.

00:05:33.016 --> 00:05:34.081
vart a bisele.

00:05:34.081 --> 00:05:37.426
 az ir zayt geven in, az ir hot gelebt bay Landmanen

00:05:37.426 --> 00:05:38.393
in Kovne

00:05:38.393 --> 00:05:39.011
ye.

00:05:38.835 --> 00:05:41.704
 vi iz gegangen ayer lebn? vos flegt ir ton?

00:05:41.704 --> 00:05:45.081
keyn zakh nit; ikh fleg (ah, arop-,) geyn shpatsirn

00:05:45.081 --> 00:05:46.688
in kino, in teater.

00:05:46.688 --> 00:05:51.048
keyn zakh (iz) mir nit gefel- dos iz shoyn geven kimat azoy vi far di krig.

00:05:51.048 --> 00:05:58.809
iz shoyn dos geven. zey, ikh hob gevelt geyn arbetn, hot der onkl mir nit gelozn, zogt er "vos darfstu arbetn, velkhe arbet, vos far a arbet?"

00:05:58.540 --> 00:06:01.236
ir hot gehat in Kovne khaveyrim, khavertes?

00:06:00.917 --> 00:06:03.819
kh'hob gehat, nu, di eygene, di eygene.

00:06:03.819 --> 00:06:04.868
ver zaynen di eygene?

00:06:04.868 --> 00:06:08.327
nu, di eygene kuzi- ku- kuzinen, kuzines.

00:06:08.327 --> 00:06:10.704
ot in teater, in kinos flegt ir geyn tsuzamen?

00:06:10.704 --> 00:06:13.294
tsuzamen ale.

00:06:13.294 --> 00:06:16.671
s'iz geven genug freylekh un gut tsu lebn.

00:06:16.671 --> 00:06:20.310
bay mayn onkl in shtub (az) ikh fleg arayngeyn, flegt mir (tsu) zayn freylekh.

00:06:20.310 --> 00:06:23.196
zey hobn gelebt zeyer raykh, zeyer sheyn.

00:06:23.196 --> 00:06:25.671
zaynen geven zeyer groyse gevirim.

00:06:25.671 --> 00:06:30.297
iz i- iz ir hot zikh nokh f- farbrakht, farbrakht mit di di mishpokhe fun onkl?

00:06:29.048 --> 00:06:30.736
yo, ye.

00:06:30.736 --> 00:06:34.154
dernokh, iz hot zikh ongehoybn shoyn di krig, UNK.

00:06:33.572 --> 00:06:35.404
UNK

00:06:34.726 --> 00:06:39.642
zikh ongehoybn di krig, zaynen mayne el- mayn foter iz geven zeyer krank.

00:06:39.654 --> 00:06:43.507
zaynen zey ge- zey hobn zey gevelt dos antloyfn in Rusland.

00:06:43.507 --> 00:06:47.179
nor in Rusland zay-, antloyfn hobn zey shoyn nit gekent.

00:06:47.179 --> 00:06:51.704
iz unter- zaynen zey geblibn unter der vegns, un az zey zaynen geblibn unter der vegns

00:06:51.704 --> 00:06:58.523
zaynen zey shoyn tsurik in Yaneve nit geforn, nor zey zaynen gekumen in Kovne vayle zey hobn gevust az ikh bin do in Kovne.

00:06:58.523 --> 00:07:01.097
un eltern tsit zikh tsu a kind.

00:07:01.097 --> 00:07:07.409
zaynen zey gekumen; ikh hob derzen mayne eltern un mayn, mayne brider un mayn shvester; kh'hob zikh zeyer derfreyt.

00:07:07.409 --> 00:07:13.950
nu, un dernokh zaynen mir geven a kurtse tsayt tsuzamen, un men hot undz arayngefirt in kovner geto.

00:07:13.950 --> 00:07:15.753
 dertseylt a bisele.

00:07:15.753 --> 00:07:20.836
ir gedenkt di tsayt ven in, Lite, in Kovne zaynen arayn di rusn

00:07:20.836 --> 00:07:22.017
in fertsikstn yor?

00:07:21.916 --> 00:07:22.630
ye.

00:07:22.603 --> 00:07:25.049
vos gedenkt ir ve- in, fun der tsayt?

00:07:25.049 --> 00:07:32.606
di rusn zaynen arayn, zaynen ale geven zeyer tsufridn; m'hot zey zeyer sheyn oyfgenumen; m'hot zey VSTRECHAET mit blumen.

00:07:32.606 --> 00:07:34.509
un s'iz, mit eyner vort

00:07:34.376 --> 00:07:39.409
ayer onkl, Landman, bay vemen hot ir gelebt, iz oykhet geven tsufridn mit di rusn?

00:07:39.409 --> 00:07:44.655
nu, efsher; ikh veys nit; ikh hob im nit gefregt. mistomen iz er nit zeyer shtark geven tsufridn!

00:07:44.655 --> 00:07:48.962
ir veyst dokh, gevirim zeyer groyse zaynen mistame nit geven zeyer shtark tsu-

00:07:48.962 --> 00:07:50.508
nor ikh hob im nit gefregt.

00:07:50.508 --> 00:07:54.380
vi bavust hobn di rusn tsugenumen di gesheftn fun di raykhe yidn.

00:07:53.753 --> 00:07:59.163
nu, bay undz UNK hobn zey keyn zakh nit natsyonalizirt, vayl es iz geven a kleyner gesheft

00:07:59.163 --> 00:08:04.015
bay mayn onkl in Yaneve, hob ikh gehat an onkl funem tatn's; hot men im alts natsyonalizirt

00:08:04.015 --> 00:08:05.107
tsugenumen, ye?

00:08:04.802 --> 00:08:06.146
tsugenumen alts.

00:08:06.146 --> 00:08:11.736
tsugenumen zayn mebl-fabrik, mit alts vos er hot gehat ongestroyet, di hayzer, mit alts, mit

00:08:11.736 --> 00:08:17.372
m'hot alts tsugenumen, un er iz ahergekumen lebn in Kovne az er zol fargesn dos vos er hot iberlebt.

00:08:16.868 --> 00:08:18.952
aha. ir gedenkt dem nomen fun dem onkl?

00:08:18.769 --> 00:08:20.593
Yankl-Leyb; kh'hob dokh geshribn.

00:08:20.593 --> 00:08:22.428
Yankl-Leyb

00:08:21.884 --> 00:08:22.620
Landman.

00:08:22.573 --> 00:08:23.642
Yankl-Leyb Landman.

00:08:23.605 --> 00:08:24.146
ye.

00:08:24.146 --> 00:08:27.114
un ir zogt az, ayer onkl

00:08:27.114 --> 00:08:29.491
hot men avekgefirt in Sibir?

00:08:29.491 --> 00:08:30.163
ver?

00:08:30.163 --> 00:08:31.968
di rusn hobn im nisht avekgefirt in Si-?

00:08:31.606 --> 00:08:32.720
neyn.

00:08:32.524 --> 00:08:33.212
neyn.

00:08:33.212 --> 00:08:36.163
zey hobn im gevelt, ober zey hobn nit bavizn.

00:08:36.163 --> 00:08:38.117
aha. di krig hot zikh ongehoybn.

00:08:37.491 --> 00:08:40.704
ye. mir zaynen shoyn dernokh geven in geto.

00:08:40.704 --> 00:08:42.784
der, der

00:08:42.015 --> 00:08:43.179
der Yankl-Leyb.

00:08:43.179 --> 00:08:46.900
un der Ya-, un der Landman, der onkl bay velkhn hot ir gelebt

00:08:46.836 --> 00:08:48.245
iz geven in Rusland.

00:08:48.245 --> 00:08:50.655
un vi, vi iz er gekumen in Rusland?

00:08:50.655 --> 00:08:53.393
zey zaynen avekgeforn. nu, ye.

00:08:52.155 --> 00:08:52.794
antlofn?

00:08:53.393 --> 00:08:56.213
zayn zun iz geven a natshalnik fun M.G.B.

00:08:56.213 --> 00:08:59.114
nit kukndik vos er iz geven a groyser gvir

00:08:59.114 --> 00:09:02.792
un zayn zun iz geven a f- a natshalnik fun M.G.B.

00:09:01.950 --> 00:09:05.148
a ongefir(er) fun melukhe-zikherkeyt-, organ, b- bay

00:09:03.589 --> 00:09:06.376
ye, der UNK hot er zey dos avekgefirt.

00:09:06.376 --> 00:09:08.021
dos iz geven ayer sh- a shvesterkind?

00:09:07.851 --> 00:09:08.490
ye.

00:09:08.490 --> 00:09:09.654
vi hot er geheysn?

00:09:09.654 --> 00:09:11.076
(Ayze)-Motke. er iz shoy-

00:09:10.556 --> 00:09:11.081
Ayze

00:09:11.081 --> 00:09:14.441
er iz shoyn geshto- er iz umgekumen in, oyfn front.

00:09:14.441 --> 00:09:16.297
Ayze-Motke iz umgekumen oyfn front.

00:09:15.654 --> 00:09:18.392
nu, lebn Meml, lebn Meml iz er gefaln.

00:09:18.392 --> 00:09:20.097
aha, farshtendlekh.

00:09:20.097 --> 00:09:23.638
ir gedenkt, dem ershtn tog fun der milkhome?

00:09:23.638 --> 00:09:25.802
nu, ikh gedenk. ikh dermon zikh.

00:09:25.802 --> 00:09:28.556
v- vos iz forgekumen? vi hot zikh oy- vi hot oysgezen...

00:09:28.556 --> 00:09:31.524
zeyer shreklekh. zeyer shreklekh.

00:09:31.524 --> 00:09:37.360
m'hot glaykh gemakht a untersheyd ver s'iz yidn un ver s'iz kristn un vos far a NATSIONAL'NOST' men iz.

00:09:37.360 --> 00:09:41.507
m'iz gega- glaykh hot men shoyn nit gelozn geyn oyf di laves a yidn.

00:09:41.507 --> 00:09:44.245
s'iz geven a, zeyer a groyser untersheyd.

00:09:44.245 --> 00:09:47.802
s'hot glaykh gefilt az es kumen di daytshn.

00:09:47.802 --> 00:09:50.343
zogt mir azoy: vi hot dos pasirt

00:09:50.343 --> 00:09:52.654
az ir hot gelebt bay ayer onkl

00:09:52.654 --> 00:09:55.638
un ir zogt az ayer onkl iz avekgeforn in Rusland.

00:09:55.638 --> 00:09:58.394
nu iz er dokh dernokh gekumen nokh der krig dort.

00:09:57.671 --> 00:10:01.539
neyn neyn, ober in, er iz in ershtn tog fun krig avekgelofn fun da-

00:10:01.162 --> 00:10:03.244
er, far di krig, un ikh bin geblibn.

00:10:03.244 --> 00:10:04.228
in zayn dire?

00:10:04.228 --> 00:10:05.048
ye.

00:10:05.048 --> 00:10:05.470
un

00:10:05.170 --> 00:10:06.595
ikh bin, ikh bin nit geforn.

00:10:06.638 --> 00:10:07.999
un ver iz geforn mit im?

00:10:07.999 --> 00:10:11.475
mit im iz geforn zayn vayb, zayn

00:10:11.475 --> 00:10:15.016
zayn tokhter, zayn zun, ot der vos iz gefaln oyfn front.

00:10:15.016 --> 00:10:17.344
un ver iz geblibn mit aykh in, in der dire?

00:10:17.344 --> 00:10:18.295
ikh aleyn.

00:10:18.295 --> 00:10:20.349
aleyn zayt ir geblibn in onkl's dire?

00:10:19.098 --> 00:10:21.557
ye (DOVOL'NO), vos iz?

00:10:21.557 --> 00:10:25.524
bin ikh shoyn geven nisht keyn kleyninke; un es zaynen dokh glaykh gekumen mayne eltern.

00:10:25.524 --> 00:10:26.606
fun Yaneve.

00:10:26.524 --> 00:10:27.130
ye.

00:10:27.130 --> 00:10:30.950
iz, ir gedenkt vi ay- vi der onkl iz avekgeforn fun danet?

00:10:30.950 --> 00:10:34.032
nu ikh ge-, ikh dermon zikh

00:10:34.032 --> 00:10:37.360
az me zey, zey zaynen dos, in di minutn zaynen zey nit gevorn.

00:10:37.360 --> 00:10:38.870
ah, dos iz in ershtn tog fun krig?

00:10:38.606 --> 00:10:39.343
ye.

00:10:39.343 --> 00:10:41.776
un zey hobn aykh forgeleygt tsu gey- forn mit zey?

00:10:41.261 --> 00:10:42.741
ney-, ikh bin nit geforn.

00:10:42.606 --> 00:10:43.595
ah, zey hobn ge-

00:10:42.930 --> 00:10:44.475
kh'hob gezogt az oybe

00:10:44.475 --> 00:10:48.294
oybe nit, vel ikh bay zey farmakhn di shtub, un ikh'l

00:10:48.294 --> 00:10:50.816
forn in Yaneve zen vu mayne eltern zaynen.

00:10:50.458 --> 00:10:51.950
tsu ayere eltern.

00:10:51.950 --> 00:10:53.463
ober s'iz oy- s'iz gevo-

00:10:53.327 --> 00:10:55.786
mayne eltern zaynen gekumen do.

00:10:55.786 --> 00:10:56.720
tsu aykh in dire?

00:10:56.720 --> 00:10:57.720
ya.

00:10:57.720 --> 00:11:01.606
zey hobn zikh dervust avu ikh bin; zaynen gekumen, ikh hob zikh zeyer derfreyt.

00:11:01.606 --> 00:11:06.325
un mir hobn gelebt a kurtse tsayt do oyf (POÅ KOS)-gas, un dernokh iz aroys a ZAKON

00:11:06.081 --> 00:11:06.737
a gezets?

00:11:06.737 --> 00:11:10.307
a gezets az me darf geyn in geto, zaynen mir avek in geto.

00:11:10.147 --> 00:11:12.376
ir hot gehat a sakh eygntum bay zikh

00:11:12.376 --> 00:11:13.769
az ir zayt geforn in geto?

00:11:13.769 --> 00:11:17.310
neyn. neyn. neyn.

00:11:17.310 --> 00:11:17.949
neyn, nu

00:11:17.949 --> 00:11:22.212
vayle mayne eltern iz, hot men shoyn fun mayne eltern hot men tsugenumen altsding in Yaneve.

00:11:22.212 --> 00:11:24.556
yo, ober aykh hot dokh ibergeblibn fun dem onkl.

00:11:24.556 --> 00:11:26.507
der onkl hot altsding mitgenumen.

00:11:26.507 --> 00:11:28.403
a vos iz nokh geven vertfule zakhn.

00:11:28.146 --> 00:11:28.982
ye.

00:11:28.982 --> 00:11:34.146
iz az ir zayt gekumen in geto, vi zayt ir gegangen, tsu fus oder mit a fur geforn?

00:11:34.146 --> 00:11:39.916
zey zaynen gegangen tsu fus in geto, iz do in Slabodke, vifl iz dos tsu forn.

00:11:39.441 --> 00:11:44.074
poshet, s'iz, di zakhn zaynen geven az m'hot dos gekent fartrogn, ye?

00:11:41.351 --> 00:11:41.872
ye.

00:11:44.074 --> 00:11:48.776
ya, ya. de- dem merstn teyl hot men altsding tsugenumen.

00:11:48.786 --> 00:11:49.769
nu, VOT.

00:11:49.769 --> 00:11:52.383
 ir zayt arayn in geto, iz

00:11:51.654 --> 00:11:57.196
(azoy) bin ikh geven in geto mit mayne eltern, mit mayne brider, mit mayn shvester.

00:11:57.196 --> 00:12:03.557
dernokh iz aro- iz aroys shoyn, iz shoyn, hobn zey gemakht dort, flegn zey di daytshn makhn ale vayle aktsyes.

00:12:03.557 --> 00:12:04.704
vos iz dos aktsyes?

00:12:04.704 --> 00:12:08.065
aktsye: me flegt aroystraybn oyfn gas

00:12:08.065 --> 00:12:11.196
un oysshteln vifl yidn zaynen do

00:12:11.196 --> 00:12:14.983
un me fleg darfn opshteyn fun in der fri biz oyf morgn.

00:12:14.983 --> 00:12:20.130
un zey flegn, zey flegn sortirn, vemen rekhts, vemen links, vemen rekhts, vemen links.

00:12:20.130 --> 00:12:24.491
un keyner hot nit gevust ts- oyf velkhe zayt dos iz, tsu s'iz di gute tsu s'iz di shlekhte.

00:12:24.491 --> 00:12:29.704
nor dernokh az s'hot (zikh) geendikt, flegt men shoyn visn ver s'iz oyf di gute zayt, ver s'iz oyf di shlekhte zayt.

00:12:29.704 --> 00:12:32.393
un mir zaynen ale gekumen oyf di gute zayt.

00:12:32.393 --> 00:12:35.250
 velkhe aktsyes gedenkt ir in kovner ge-

00:12:34.688 --> 00:12:36.822
ikh gedenk oto di-o get- ot-o

00:12:36.853 --> 00:12:41.098
di-o aktsye gedenk ikh ven m'hot undz alemen aroysgetribn un m'iz opgeshtorbn

00:12:41.098 --> 00:12:44.196
opgeshtanen a gantsn tog mit a gantse nakht.

00:12:44.196 --> 00:12:46.458
un zaynen gesortirt.

00:12:46.458 --> 00:12:49.065
gesortirt vemen rekhts, vemen links.

00:12:49.065 --> 00:12:55.163
zaynen mir ale gekumen tsu geyn, mayne eltern un mayn, mayne brider un mayn shves- nor eyn

00:12:55.163 --> 00:12:58.458
eyn, eyn bruder iz shoyn nit geven mit undz, vayl er iz

00:12:58.458 --> 00:13:03.245
m'hot zikh funandergeteylt tsu geyn oyf di aktsyes; er iz gegangen mit mayn

00:13:03.245 --> 00:13:10.048
mit mayne a tantn mit di, mit di plimenikes, mit alemen, un er iz tsulib zey avek oyfn nayntn fort.

00:13:10.048 --> 00:13:12.860
dos heyst ayer bruder iz gegangen in an ander kolone.

00:13:12.639 --> 00:13:14.028
yo. iz er avek.

00:13:13.723 --> 00:13:14.957
in an ander rey, yo?

00:13:14.507 --> 00:13:17.503
ye, iz er avek tsulib zey oyfn nayntn fort.

00:13:17.162 --> 00:13:19.478
hot men im opgesortirt oyf di shlekhte zayt.

00:13:19.015 --> 00:13:21.933
oyf di shlekhte zayt, un er iz avek oyfn nayntn fort.

00:13:21.638 --> 00:13:24.933
umgefer ged- gedenkt ir ven iz forgekumen di aktsye?

00:13:24.933 --> 00:13:31.179
neyn, ikh gedenk nit, epes oykhet s'iz shoyn geven kalt ot azoy vi in oktyober zol ikh volt ikh zogn.

00:13:31.179 --> 00:13:33.917
vi hot geheysn di aktsye?

00:13:33.917 --> 00:13:35.556
nu, a gr- a aktsye.

00:13:35.556 --> 00:13:38.294
an aktsye, ye. ir gedenkt nor eyn aktsye in geto?

00:13:38.294 --> 00:13:42.081
eyn, UNK s'iz geven a sakh, nor oyf di bin ikh geven.

00:13:42.081 --> 00:13:43.310
oyf di bin ikh geven.

00:13:43.310 --> 00:13:46.655
un velkhe, velkhe veyst ir, fun velkhe aktsyes veyst ir nokh?

00:13:46.655 --> 00:13:49.245
nu, zey flegn oft makhn

00:13:49.245 --> 00:13:53.065
zey flegn onfaln, zey flegn tsunemen, vemen vayter, vemen

00:13:53.065 --> 00:13:57.196
zey flegn aleyn makhn, di daytshn, vemen ariberlozn oyf di gute, vemen oyf di shlekhte

00:13:57.196 --> 00:14:00.081
nor ikh fleg ale mol aribergeyn oyf di gute.

00:14:00.081 --> 00:14:05.311
zogt mir, di ershte teg; gedenkt ir ayere di ershte teg in geto?

00:14:05.311 --> 00:14:08.884
nu, ikh ts- gedenk shoyn oyf azoy vayt nit.

00:14:08.884 --> 00:14:10.441
vu hot ir gelebt in geto?

00:14:10.441 --> 00:14:11.950
oyf KRIUKU-gas

00:14:11.950 --> 00:14:13.654
KRIUKU-gas, ye?

00:14:13.654 --> 00:14:16.041
dos iz geven di groyse geto oder di kleyne geto?

00:14:15.950 --> 00:14:20.720
dos iz geven di zelbe zakh; ale di getos iz geven vos far a groyse, vos far a kleyne?

00:14:20.720 --> 00:14:23.900
ikh hob gelebt oyf KRIUKU-gas, KRIUKU nayn.

00:14:23.900 --> 00:14:26.488
KRIUKU-gas nayn, yo? tsuzamen mit ayere eltern.

00:14:26.327 --> 00:14:27.130
ya.

00:14:27.572 --> 00:14:28.459
un dernokh

00:14:28.459 --> 00:14:34.363
hob ikh khasene gehat, un ikh hob shoyn gelebt mit mayn man, mit m- bay mayne eltern, mit alemen tsuzamen.

00:14:34.245 --> 00:14:36.836
bay ayere eltern hot ir gelebt tsu di, bay di man's eltern?

00:14:36.836 --> 00:14:38.475
bay di, bay mayne eltern.

00:14:38.475 --> 00:14:39.770
tsuzamen mitn man?

00:14:39.770 --> 00:14:43.245
ye. dernokh hot men mayne eltern tsugenumen.

00:14:43.245 --> 00:14:44.835
vu hot men tsugenumen ayere eltern?

00:14:44.835 --> 00:14:46.015
oyf Estland.

00:14:46.015 --> 00:14:48.909
ah, az s'iz geven der iberzidlung oyf Estland hot men

00:14:48.048 --> 00:14:54.786
yo, hot men tsugenumen mayn foter un mayn muter un mayn shvester, un der elterer bruder iz geven aroysgeshikt bay daytshn

00:14:54.786 --> 00:14:56.835
in a brigade tsum arbetn.

00:14:56.835 --> 00:14:58.797
ober i- im hot men nisht genumen in Es-

00:14:58.409 --> 00:15:00.802
az er, er iz dokh nit geven in shtub.

00:15:00.802 --> 00:15:02.648
un aykh hot men oykh nisht genumen oyf Es-

00:15:02.032 --> 00:15:05.261
mir hot men nit genumen, vayl ikh bin shoyn geven oyf mayn man's familye.

00:15:05.261 --> 00:15:09.753
 zogt mir azoy, az, di ershte teg fun geto, di ershte khadoshim fun geto

00:15:09.753 --> 00:15:13.048
flegt ir geyn, ayere eltern flegn geyn arbetn?

00:15:13.048 --> 00:15:15.819
mayne eltern, zey hobn nit gearbet in geto.

00:15:15.819 --> 00:15:16.475
neyn?

00:15:16.367 --> 00:15:17.419
neyn, s'iz nit geve-

00:15:16.753 --> 00:15:17.638
ir hot gearbet?

00:15:17.638 --> 00:15:19.507
ikh hob gearbet oyfn flugplats.

00:15:19.507 --> 00:15:20.704
oyfn erodrom.

00:15:20.704 --> 00:15:23.409
ir flegt geyn arbetn oyfn aerodrom yedn tog?

00:15:23.409 --> 00:15:24.802
yedn tog.

00:15:24.802 --> 00:15:26.970
vos flegt ir ton dortn, in, in ayere

00:15:26.393 --> 00:15:30.360
shitn in di vagonetkes di erd.

00:15:30.360 --> 00:15:33.179
un dernokh hob ikh gearbet oyf a gortn

00:15:33.179 --> 00:15:35.376
ot mit ayer muter tsuzamen.

00:15:35.376 --> 00:15:38.136
vos, vos flegt ir ton oyfn, oyfn gortn?

00:15:37.901 --> 00:15:42.359
oyfn gortn? vos me tut oyf a gortn, me flegt polenen, ramen, makhn,

00:15:42.359 --> 00:15:46.900
di bulves flegn mir helfn aropnemen, flegt forn a mashin un mir hinter zey.

00:15:46.900 --> 00:15:49.480
vifl a zeyger flegt ir darfn aroysgeyn oyf der arbet?

00:15:49.228 --> 00:15:52.244
oyf der arbet? baginen. fintster baginen.

00:15:52.244 --> 00:15:53.900
ir gedenkt vifl umgefer a zeyger?

00:15:53.605 --> 00:15:56.917
nu, umgefer a zeyger zeks in der fri gevis.

00:15:56.917 --> 00:15:58.770
un ven flegt ir zikh umkern aheym?

00:15:58.770 --> 00:15:59.819
far nakht.

00:15:59.819 --> 00:16:01.688
far nakht, ye?

00:16:01.688 --> 00:16:03.216
fun flugplats far nakht.

00:16:02.999 --> 00:16:06.458
un vos, ah, a gantsn tog hot ir epes gegesn? ir hot gehat mit zikh?

00:16:06.458 --> 00:16:09.065
mir flegn nit hobn vos tsum esn.

00:16:09.065 --> 00:16:14.049
az mir flegn hobn vos in shtub tsum esn flegn mir mitnemen; az s'flegt nit zayn, flegt men UNK

00:16:14.049 --> 00:16:16.213
zayn hungerik a gantsn tog.

00:16:16.213 --> 00:16:19.885
oyfn erodrom flegt men gebn a mol hundert fuftsik gram broyt.

00:16:19.885 --> 00:16:20.934
mitog, yo?

00:16:20.934 --> 00:16:23.688
ye, nor ikh fleg di broyt nit oyfesn,

00:16:23.688 --> 00:16:27.065
fleg avektrogn far mayn foter.

00:16:27.065 --> 00:16:31.360
 aykh iz oysgekumen, tsu, fun arbetn oyf di gertner

00:16:31.360 --> 00:16:33.393
vos nit iz tsuganvenen bay di daytshn?

00:16:33.393 --> 00:16:36.639
nu, ikh fleg a mol nemen dortn az me flegt kenen.

00:16:36.639 --> 00:16:38.573
ugerkes, bulves.

00:16:38.573 --> 00:16:43.081
me flegt undz lozn a mol, der daytsh, nemen bulves, un az er flegt vern in kas

00:16:43.081 --> 00:16:46.065
flegt er nit lozn ot vos dos iz vert nemen.

00:16:46.065 --> 00:16:49.278
un ah, dos iz ge- aykh iz dos gelungen arayntrogn in geto?

00:16:49.278 --> 00:16:51.016
ye.

00:16:51.016 --> 00:16:53.639
ikh bin geven a dreyste zeyer.

00:16:53.639 --> 00:16:56.688
ikh bin nit geven vi itster.

00:16:56.688 --> 00:17:01.049
 un, mi- fun vos hot ayer mishpokhe gelebt in geto?

00:17:01.049 --> 00:17:02.639
fun vos hot men gelebt?

00:17:02.639 --> 00:17:08.032
fun dos vos me flegt hobn, a vos nit iz a zakh, vos m'hot gehat, flegt men farkoyfn un, un lebn.

00:17:08.032 --> 00:17:11.622
ir gedenkt vi, ir, az ir zolt farkoyfn epes a zakh?

00:17:11.622 --> 00:17:15.048
ikh fleg nit farkoyfn; mayn elterer bruder flegt dos farkoyfn.

00:17:15.048 --> 00:17:17.310
vi flegt er dos farkoyfn?

00:17:17.310 --> 00:17:18.638
bay di litviner.

00:17:18.638 --> 00:17:21.458
 v- vu hot er gehat a kontakt mit di litviner?

00:17:21.458 --> 00:17:25.179
er hot gearbet in drite COMPAGNIE bay di daytshn

00:17:25.179 --> 00:17:29.671
flegt er zikh, b- opbetn baym daytsh avekgeyn un farkoyfn vos me fleg darfn.

00:17:29.671 --> 00:17:31.760
un er vet, brengen in g- geto shpayz?

00:17:31.687 --> 00:17:32.917
ye.

00:17:32.917 --> 00:17:34.556
aykh hot geklekt shpayz in geto?

00:17:34.556 --> 00:17:40.032
nu, nit zeyer. me flegt di ershte tsaytn hobn mir gelitn hunger.

00:17:40.032 --> 00:17:44.114
dernokh az me flegt shoyn vos nit iz farkoyfn un brengen, flegt dos shoyn zayn

00:17:44.114 --> 00:17:47.638
halb hungerik. halb hungerik.

00:17:47.638 --> 00:17:49.884
ikh hob nit opgegesn vi me darf.

00:17:49.884 --> 00:17:51.867
i- ayer mishpokhe in geto

00:17:51.867 --> 00:17:54.359
ir hot gehat eyn tsimer in geto?

00:17:54.359 --> 00:17:57.572
dortn iz geven, tsvey tsimerlekh kleyninke.

00:17:57.572 --> 00:18:00.605
far a- un vifl perzon zayt ir geven in di tsvey tsimerlekh?

00:18:00.605 --> 00:18:03.671
 zaynen mir geven mir zeks.

00:18:03.671 --> 00:18:07.130
un dernokh zaynen geven mayne beyde kuzines nokh, zalbe akht.

00:18:07.130 --> 00:18:09.090
zalbe akht in tsvey kleyninke tsimer.

00:18:08.343 --> 00:18:11.558
ye, zalbe naynt, zalbe tsent, ver gedenkt dos?

00:18:11.195 --> 00:18:13.917
un fun vanet, flegt ir nemen, vaser?

00:18:13.917 --> 00:18:16.982
vaser?, flegn, flegt zayn a brunem.

00:18:16.982 --> 00:18:18.460
 lebn shtub, ya?

00:18:18.048 --> 00:18:19.146
ya.

00:18:19.146 --> 00:18:21.835
un vu iz geven der tualet?

00:18:21.835 --> 00:18:25.113
der tualet iz geven in hoyf azelkhene gemakhte.

00:18:25.113 --> 00:18:27.340
gemakhte baydlekh azelkhene, yo?

00:18:26.917 --> 00:18:28.232
ye, ye.

00:18:28.232 --> 00:18:30.441
itster dertseylt mir a bisele

00:18:30.441 --> 00:18:32.950
vegn ayer man's mishpokhe.

00:18:32.950 --> 00:18:36.468
nu vos zol ikh aykh dertseyln vegn mayn man's? keyner iz nit geblibn fun zey.

00:18:36.344 --> 00:18:40.999
neyn, neyn, ikh farshtey, ober far der milkhome mit vos hot zikh farnumen zayn mishpokhe? fun vanet shtamt er?

00:18:40.999 --> 00:18:44.327
er iz geven in Pariz aleyn, hob ikh dokh aykh gezogt.

00:18:44.327 --> 00:18:48.827
un dernokh iz er gekumen do tsu forn, un vayter

00:18:47.999 --> 00:18:48.884
in velkhn yor?

00:18:48.884 --> 00:18:53.195
gedenk ikh nit, kh'veys dos nit. er er UNK (hot) azoy dertseylt.

00:18:53.195 --> 00:18:56.884
un dernokh iz er tsurik avekgeforn UNK un az s'hot zikh ongehoybn

00:18:56.884 --> 00:19:00.606
di krig in Frankraykh dortn, zaynen zey gekumen do tsu forn in Lite.

00:19:00.606 --> 00:19:03.147
vayle di mame zayne iz geven fun Lite.

00:19:03.147 --> 00:19:06.425
zi hot do gehat a shvester mit a bruder.

00:19:06.425 --> 00:19:09.573
zaynen zey gekumen tsu forn, un zey hobn shoyn gelebt in Lite.

00:19:08.917 --> 00:19:11.343
iz ayer man iz geven g- a gebildeter mentsh?

00:19:11.343 --> 00:19:13.950
nu, TAK SEBE.

00:19:13.950 --> 00:19:17.547
veys nit vos er hot geendikt, ven er hot geendikt, vos er hot geendikt veys ikh nit.

00:19:17.294 --> 00:19:20.507
un vos er hot geton in Pariz sh- hot aykh, der man dertseylt?

00:19:20.507 --> 00:19:21.980
vos er hot geton?

00:19:21.934 --> 00:19:22.327
yo.

00:19:21.980 --> 00:19:24.344
er hot gelernt nokh, er iz dokh geven a yunger.

00:19:24.344 --> 00:19:25.880
vu er hot gelernt in

00:19:25.048 --> 00:19:29.818
un dernokh hot er zikh oysgelernt a fakh, a shveyser iz er geven, ir veyst dokh aza

00:19:29.818 --> 00:19:31.884
er flegt mit briln azelkhene

00:19:31.884 --> 00:19:34.999
ah, shveysn azelkhene zakhn; er flegt fardinen zeyer a sakh.

00:19:34.999 --> 00:19:37.704
a sh- vo- metal flegt er shveysn?

00:19:36.759 --> 00:19:37.429
ya.

00:19:37.704 --> 00:19:39.704
aha. un dos iz geven zayn fakh.

00:19:39.704 --> 00:19:41.950
dos iz geven zayn fakh.

00:19:41.950 --> 00:19:42.687
un az

00:19:42.687 --> 00:19:46.917
ikh vil zikh nit rimen; er iz geven zeyer a guter mentsh un zeyer a sheyner.

00:19:46.917 --> 00:19:48.737
vu hot ir zikh bakant mit ayer man?

00:19:48.737 --> 00:19:49.983
in geto.

00:19:49.983 --> 00:19:50.704
in geto?

00:19:51.262 --> 00:19:53.606
un, un in geto

00:19:53.606 --> 00:19:58.753
nu, ikh hob dem, in geto hob ikh khasene gehat; ikh hob nit gevelt khasene hobn, nor mayn onkl zogt

00:19:58.753 --> 00:20:02.917
"vos vestu" zogt er; er hot dokh nit farshtanen az mir veln umkumen, az

00:20:02.917 --> 00:20:06.671
az s'vet zayn azoy az mir darfn umkumen az s'vet keyn zakh nit zayn,

00:20:06.671 --> 00:20:09.425
zogt er "nokh di krig vestu zayn an oreme

00:20:09.425 --> 00:20:14.589
un vu vestu azoy gikh khasene hobn, un do aza min yung, aza min sheyner, aza min guter" zogt er.

00:20:14.589 --> 00:20:18.360
"hob khasene shoyn, vos far a untersheyd, geto, nit geto."

00:20:18.360 --> 00:20:20.230
hob ikh dan khasene gehat.

00:20:19.425 --> 00:20:22.097
in vi iz, vi hot oysgezen di khasene in geto?

00:20:22.097 --> 00:20:30.325
di khasene in geto? nu, mir hobn azoy keyn zakh nit gemakht. nor far eygene; mitog un erleydikt, avek zikh opgeshribn, in geto geven vu zikh optsushraybn

00:20:30.080 --> 00:20:31.570
vu, vu hot ir zi-

00:20:30.589 --> 00:20:33.409
in a komitet, in komitet iz dos geven aza min

00:20:33.409 --> 00:20:36.196
ir gedenkt d- dem tog fun ayer opshraybn zikh?

00:20:36.196 --> 00:20:39.786
ikh hob shoyn fargesn; fregt dos nit!

00:20:39.786 --> 00:20:43.654
yo, vi ir, ir, vi ir hot gegangen, vi ir zayt gegangen in komitet gedenkt ir?

00:20:43.654 --> 00:20:46.245
dos gedenk ikh, ober dem tog gedenk ikh nit.

00:20:46.245 --> 00:20:48.294
aha. un, un ver hot aykh opgeshribn?

00:20:48.294 --> 00:20:53.223
nu? spetsyel iz dortn geven azelkhene mentshn vos zey hobn zikh farnumen mit dem in Kovne.

00:20:52.409 --> 00:20:54.261
m'hot aykh vos nit iz gezogt bay dem?

00:20:54.261 --> 00:20:55.572
nu, (to) farshteyt zikh.

00:20:55.572 --> 00:20:57.441
un a tsetl hot men aykh gegebn?

00:20:57.441 --> 00:21:00.228
keyne tsetele nit; m'hot opgeshribn un erleydikt.

00:21:00.228 --> 00:21:02.070
un ir zayt gevorn man un froy.

00:21:01.867 --> 00:21:05.130
ye, un es iz, geven eydes.

00:21:05.130 --> 00:21:09.572
eydes fun zayn zayt, eydes fun mayn zayt. fun mayn zayt iz geven mayn mame's a

00:21:09.572 --> 00:21:16.113
a fraynt; er iz shoyn nito oyf der velt. er iz gegangen far mir far an eydes, un far im gedenk ikh nit ver s'iz gegangen.

00:21:16.113 --> 00:21:18.327
ayer man hot gehat oykhet a mishpokhe in geto?

00:21:18.327 --> 00:21:21.655
nu, a foter mit a muter mit a shvester.

00:21:21.655 --> 00:21:25.278
un, ober nokh der khasene iz ayer man avek lebn tsu aykh?

00:21:25.278 --> 00:21:27.671
nu, (to) farshteyt zikh.

00:21:27.671 --> 00:21:32.098
er iz di gantse tsayt geven mit mir biz vanet mir zaynen gekumen in STUTTHOF.

00:21:32.098 --> 00:21:33.314
ah dan hot

00:21:32.570 --> 00:21:37.835
in STUTTHOF hot men undz opgesheydt, un fun dan on hob ikh im shoyn mer keyn mol nit gezen.

00:21:37.835 --> 00:21:39.300
iz, ah

00:21:38.638 --> 00:21:41.917
eyn mol hot er shoyn dortn UNK dortn UNK shoyn funandergesheydt.

00:21:41.917 --> 00:21:47.868
iz, dertseylt, dertseylt a bisl vi s'iz gegangen ayer lebn in algemeyn, d- mit der mishpokhe?

00:21:47.868 --> 00:21:49.150
mit velkhe mishpokhe?

00:21:48.786 --> 00:21:52.530
mi- a- ir o- der man, der tate, di muter, der bruder?

00:21:51.753 --> 00:21:59.015
nu oh, to vos ken, vos ho- vos hot undz gekent geyn, nu vos hot gekent geyn az m'hot gelebt in azelkhene tsores?

00:21:59.015 --> 00:22:02.146
se flegt zayn fintster un biter.

00:22:02.146 --> 00:22:05.769
mir zaynen gekumen in, in, dos iz STUTTHOF, iz aroys a ba-

00:22:05.769 --> 00:22:09.917
a ZAKON az di froyen zoln zayn bazunder un di mener bazunder.

00:22:09.917 --> 00:22:13.720
un fun dan hot men im tsum- o- tsugenumen, un mer hob ikh im shoyn nit gezen.

00:22:13.720 --> 00:22:17.670
yo, ober, un in geto, in geto flegt ayer man arbetn vos nit iz?

00:22:17.507 --> 00:22:18.950
er hot gearbet.

00:22:18.950 --> 00:22:26.130
er hot gearbet bay di daytshn. keyn gelt flegt er dort, flegt men dokh nit tsoln. me flegt dokh undz keyn gelt nit tsoln; mir zaynen dokh geven heftlinger.

00:22:26.130 --> 00:22:28.966
me flegt geyn mit di lates oyfn rukn.

00:22:28.966 --> 00:22:33.010
an- az ir hot khasene gehat, flegt ir vayter oykh geyn arbetn oyfn aerodrom?

00:22:32.917 --> 00:22:34.097
di gantse tsayt.

00:22:34.097 --> 00:22:34.970
un

00:22:34.884 --> 00:22:38.490
(az eyne-) me flegt nit geyn arbetn flegt men araynzetsn in kartser.

00:22:38.490 --> 00:22:39.229
in geto.

00:22:39.229 --> 00:22:40.442
ya.

00:22:40.442 --> 00:22:44.323
un zogt mir, arbetn hot men gedarft geyn yeder tog tsi yedn tsveytn tog?

00:22:43.868 --> 00:22:46.081
yedn tog, yedn tog.

00:22:45.868 --> 00:22:47.081
un zuntik?

00:22:47.081 --> 00:22:48.901
nu, zuntik nit.

00:22:48.901 --> 00:22:50.646
zuntik flegt men nit geyn arbetn.

00:22:50.426 --> 00:22:51.409
neyn.

00:22:51.409 --> 00:22:52.393
zeks

00:22:51.670 --> 00:22:54.420
UNK zeks teg flegt men arbet(n).

00:22:54.229 --> 00:22:56.120
zuntik iz geven a, a

00:22:55.655 --> 00:22:58.210
ye, shabes nit, shabes m'hot gearbet.

00:22:57.664 --> 00:22:58.901
shabes flegt men arbetn.

00:22:58.901 --> 00:23:02.690
ye. m'hot gearbet a gantse

00:23:02.032 --> 00:23:04.409
ir gedenkt, ayer (kolone) iz geven a groyse

00:23:04.409 --> 00:23:06.612
vos zi fleg geyn arbetn oyfn aerodrom?

00:23:06.491 --> 00:23:10.081
zeyer a groyse; zeyer a sakh mentshn.

00:23:10.081 --> 00:23:13.851
merstn teyl zaynen gegangen oyfn aerodrom.

00:23:13.851 --> 00:23:19.523
ver s'hot nit gehat keyn bakantshaft iz gegangen oyfn aerodrom; ver es gehat bakantshaft iz gegangen in brigades.

00:23:19.523 --> 00:23:21.786
ayer man iz nisht gegangen oyfn aerodrom.

00:23:21.786 --> 00:23:22.736
neyn.

00:23:22.736 --> 00:23:23.406
vu hot

00:23:22.890 --> 00:23:25.245
UNK er hot ge- er hot gehat aza fakh.

00:23:25.245 --> 00:23:31.586
un di daytshn zaynen gekumen un zey hobn gefregt ver es, ver es ken aza fakh hobn zey im genumen arbetn.

00:23:31.586 --> 00:23:32.556
iz, vu hot gear-

00:23:32.160 --> 00:23:37.257
fun, er hot gearbet in driter COMPAGNIE mit mayn eltern bruder; fun dan hob ikh zikh dort bakant mit im.

00:23:37.081 --> 00:23:38.048
durkhn bruder.

00:23:38.048 --> 00:23:38.687
ya.

00:23:38.687 --> 00:23:40.736
der, der bruder hot aykh ba- bakant gemakht?

00:23:40.736 --> 00:23:42.523
er hot im gebrakht bay undz in shtub.

00:23:42.523 --> 00:23:44.327
er iz gekumen tsu im vi a khaver.

00:23:44.327 --> 00:23:44.933
aha.

00:23:44.933 --> 00:23:45.720
nu.

00:23:45.720 --> 00:23:48.040
un azoy hot ir zikh bakant mit ayer tsukunftikn man.

00:23:47.556 --> 00:23:48.901
ya, ya.

00:23:48.901 --> 00:23:51.336
vos zayn familye-nomen iz geven Rabinovitsh.

00:23:50.672 --> 00:23:52.180
ya.

00:23:52.180 --> 00:23:54.934
geven zeyer a guter mentsh, halevay volt er gelebt.

00:23:54.934 --> 00:23:58.917
vos, vos hobn zey get- vos hobn zey geton in der brigade?

00:23:58.917 --> 00:24:01.710
in brigade hobn zey gearbet bay zeyer fakh.

00:24:01.710 --> 00:24:03.261
bay zeyer fakh.

00:24:03.261 --> 00:24:06.212
s'iz geven tsveyte COMPAGNIE, drite COMPAGNIE.

00:24:06.212 --> 00:24:11.212
mayn bruder iz geven a stolyer; hot er gearbet in tsvey- in drite COMPAGNIE far a stolyer.

00:24:11.212 --> 00:24:14.966
mayn yingerer bruder vos iz umgekumen, er hot gearbet far a

00:24:14.966 --> 00:24:18.343
oykhet in, tsveyte COMPAGNIE, oykh far a stolyer.

00:24:18.343 --> 00:24:20.049
zey flegn kumen di daytshn un

00:24:20.049 --> 00:24:23.950
fregn ver s'iz a tishler, ver s'iz aza min fakh, aza min fakh.

00:24:23.950 --> 00:24:26.967
flegt men fregn un zey avekgenumen arbetn.

00:24:26.967 --> 00:24:30.110
aha. un ah, zey flegn arbetn far di daytshn in di kompanyes?

00:24:29.934 --> 00:24:33.639
ye, keyn gelt flegn zey derfar nit krign, keyne gelt nit.

00:24:33.639 --> 00:24:37.803
vayle keyn gelt hot men dokh undz nit getsolt, mir zaynen dokh geven heftlinger.

00:24:37.803 --> 00:24:39.983
vosere gelt, velkhe gelt?

00:24:39.983 --> 00:24:42.475
ober, dortn bay der arbet

00:24:42.475 --> 00:24:44.311
flegn zey epes baytn zakhn.

00:24:44.311 --> 00:24:51.556
nu, zey flegn betn zey- vi me- az arbetn vi flegt men zikh shoyn aynlebn mit di daytshn, flegt men shoyn vern

00:24:51.556 --> 00:24:54.868
GUT BRUDER, flegt men shoyn, flegn zey dos aroyslozn.

00:24:54.868 --> 00:25:00.802
ober onzogn az, zey zoln nor nit zogn az er hot aroysgelozn, az m'hot nit gezen vi er iz aroys

00:25:00.802 --> 00:25:02.064
ir farshteyt?

00:25:02.064 --> 00:25:03.963
az, az tomer vos,

00:25:03.754 --> 00:25:04.852
zol men nit zogn.

00:25:04.852 --> 00:25:06.594
zol der daytsh zayn umshuldik.

00:25:06.393 --> 00:25:09.754
er zol nit zayn umshuldik, vayl az nit vet men dokh im opshisn.

00:25:10.333 --> 00:25:12.290
nu, ot azoy iz dos geven

00:25:11.469 --> 00:25:16.137
ober, say dem bruder say der man, zey zaynen nit durkhgefaln bay, bay dem zakh.

00:25:15.835 --> 00:25:19.557
neyn, neyn. nisht (geven) UNK durkhfaln bay di zakh.

00:25:19.557 --> 00:25:23.589
ikh aleyn fleg antloyfn fun lager, un ikh bin geblibn lebn.

00:25:23.589 --> 00:25:26.888
 ober fun geto, fun aerodrom flegt ir nisht loyfn?

00:25:26.888 --> 00:25:28.507
neyn. gor nit.

00:25:28.507 --> 00:25:34.196
mir zaynen shoyn geku- av- aroy- az me hot undz shoyn avekgefirt fun geto, un ikh bin geven shoyn in Daytshland.

00:25:34.196 --> 00:25:35.870
a dan flegt ir loyfn, yo?

00:25:35.409 --> 00:25:40.425
dan, ikh bin shoyn geven in Daytshland, hot men undz gebrakht tsu firn, iz nor geven

00:25:40.425 --> 00:25:44.819
un me flegt zikh nor zen himl un vaser, vaser un himl.

00:25:44.819 --> 00:25:49.344
un fun vaytn flegt men zikh zen a por shtiblekh, etlekhe shtiblekh.

00:25:49.344 --> 00:25:56.983
un ikh bin shoyn geven dortn bay di, in di, in lager, un m'iz geven zeyer hungerik vayle vos tsu gebn esn hobn zey nit gehat

00:25:56.983 --> 00:26:03.480
flegn zey gebn eyn bulve a tog tsvey bulves a tog, ken men lebn mit UNK ikh bin dan dokh geven a yunge; kh'hob nor gevelt esn

00:26:04.852 --> 00:26:11.573
fleg, hob ikh eyn mol gekukt, gekukt, gekukt, trakht ikh vi s'vet zayn vet zayn; ikh'l oprizikirn un avekgeyn in shtetl.

00:26:11.573 --> 00:26:13.003
oder lebn oder toyt.

00:26:12.901 --> 00:26:14.114
dos iz shoyn zayendik in lager?

00:26:14.114 --> 00:26:14.606
ya.

00:26:14.606 --> 00:26:17.376
dos vet ir dertseyln nokh dem. itster dertseylt a bisl

00:26:17.376 --> 00:26:22.245
vi s'hot oysgezen, vi gedenkt ir, ir gedenkt vi m- ayere eltern hot men avekgefirt in Estonye

00:26:22.245 --> 00:26:28.409
nu, iz dos gedenk ikh, ober vos dortn iz geven mit zey, ven s'iz geven mit zey veys ikh nit vayle ikh veys dos vos me hot mir dertseylt.

00:26:28.409 --> 00:26:31.702
yo ober, vi ir, ir hot zikh gezegnt mit zey gedenkt ir?

00:26:30.835 --> 00:26:33.245
gezegnt. dos gedenk ikh.

00:26:33.245 --> 00:26:38.444
ayere eltern un ayere shvester hobn gevust fun foroys az me vet zay aroysfirn in Estonye?

00:26:38.195 --> 00:26:42.100
m'hot gevust; m'hot dokh fun der, fun komitet gezogt, gegebn di

00:26:41.392 --> 00:26:44.160
mit vifl teg umgefer frier hot ir gevust az ir ve-

00:26:42.999 --> 00:26:47.671
nu, mit a, mit a tog, mit a t- mit a por sho frier, mit dray sho frier.

00:26:47.671 --> 00:26:49.540
hot men gezogt az,

00:26:49.540 --> 00:26:55.802
ye, az me zol zikh tsunoyfnemen un me firt avek. me hot zey nit gezogt avu me firt, az me firt dos aroys oyf der arbet.

00:26:52.425 --> 00:26:52.772
u-

00:26:55.802 --> 00:26:57.607
in an ander or- in an ander gegnt.

00:26:57.349 --> 00:26:58.153
ye.

00:26:58.153 --> 00:27:01.622
ober i- ir hot gevust az me firt in Estonye, az me firt in Estland?

00:27:01.622 --> 00:27:02.393
neyn.

00:27:02.393 --> 00:27:03.606
neyn, ir ge- ir hot

00:27:03.606 --> 00:27:05.688
ir hot gevust nor az me firt zey aroys fun geto.

00:27:05.688 --> 00:27:07.569
ye. mer keyn zakh nit.

00:27:07.376 --> 00:27:11.456
un az ir mitn bl- az ir mitn man blaybt iber in, in geto.

00:27:10.819 --> 00:27:13.753
ye. ikh hob gevolt forn mit di eltern.

00:27:13.753 --> 00:27:16.639
o- hobn, hobn zey mir nit gelozn.

00:27:16.639 --> 00:27:17.868
ver, di eltern?

00:27:17.868 --> 00:27:18.737
ye.

00:27:18.737 --> 00:27:20.990
zey hobn aykh iberge- ibergelozn mitn

00:27:20.262 --> 00:27:23.540
ikh hob gevelt iberlozn dem man un forn mit di eltern.

00:27:23.540 --> 00:27:26.180
kh'hob zeyer fil geveynt, zeyer

00:27:26.180 --> 00:27:30.999
ikh reyd, es kost mir gezunt, ikh ken nit reydn keyn sakh.

00:27:30.999 --> 00:27:32.490
yo, ir

00:27:32.213 --> 00:27:36.950
mayne eltern hobn mir nit gelozn for- zey hobn gezogt "du host a man un blayb mit dayn man."

00:27:36.950 --> 00:27:37.970
un, ze-

00:27:37.622 --> 00:27:39.376
er hot zey, er hot zey dos gebetn.

00:27:39.376 --> 00:27:41.500
der man hot dos gebetn, az, zey

00:27:41.343 --> 00:27:43.065
az zey zoln mir nit nemen.

00:27:43.065 --> 00:27:46.015
aha, un un zey zaynen ayngegangen oyf dem

00:27:46.015 --> 00:27:51.622
nu farshteyt, az tate-mame, vos tuen nit far kinder?

00:27:51.622 --> 00:27:57.966
un ah, vifl, vifl ayer mishpokhe-mitglider zaynen (avekgeforn) di tate, di mame, di yingere shvester?

00:27:57.966 --> 00:28:02.147
zaynen di yingere shvester mitn tatn mit di mamen zaynen avekgeforn tsuzamen.

00:28:02.147 --> 00:28:04.330
tsuzamen in, in Estland.

00:28:04.180 --> 00:28:06.684
nu, ikh hob nit gevust tsu dos, oyf Estland tsu (vu)

00:28:06.213 --> 00:28:08.140
ye. dernokh hot ir zikh d-

00:28:07.392 --> 00:28:09.770
dernokh hob ikh zikh dervust.

00:28:09.770 --> 00:28:13.294
yo, un, un ir iz, un mer hot ir zey shoyn keyn mol nisht gezen.

00:28:13.294 --> 00:28:15.294
neyn.

00:28:15.294 --> 00:28:18.409
dray teg far di bafrayung hot men zey farbrent.

00:28:18.409 --> 00:28:21.261
ah, ir hot dos, ir hot zikh der- dervust

00:28:21.261 --> 00:28:25.130
fun a kuzin. er iz itster in Erets-Yisroel. ikh veys nit tsu er lebt tsu er lebt nit.

00:28:25.130 --> 00:28:28.064
a gevezener kuzin; di kuzine iz shoyn umgekumen in

00:28:28.064 --> 00:28:29.720
dos iz a kuzine's man geven, ye?

00:28:29.474 --> 00:28:31.917
ye, in lager hot men ir farbrent, di kuzine.

00:28:31.917 --> 00:28:33.245
in, in STUTTHOF.

00:28:33.245 --> 00:28:37.967
aha. un un er iz geblibn in, un der kuzine's man iz geblibn in Estland?

00:28:37.967 --> 00:28:39.290
neyn. er

00:28:38.819 --> 00:28:41.864
fun vanet hot er gevust vegn dem goyrl fun ayer mishpokhe?

00:28:41.754 --> 00:28:47.113
fun vanet hot er gevust? vayle er iz geven tsuzamen mit mayn, mit mayn bruder in eyn lager.

00:28:47.113 --> 00:28:49.080
in vu, in, in vos far a lager?

00:28:48.622 --> 00:28:49.605
in Dakhau.

00:28:49.605 --> 00:28:51.048
un er iz geblibn lebn?

00:28:51.048 --> 00:28:52.540
ye.

00:28:52.540 --> 00:28:55.933
ah. itster, ir gedenkt dem tog

00:28:55.933 --> 00:28:59.933
vi m'hot aykh fun kovner geto avekgefirt in STUTTHOF?

00:28:59.933 --> 00:29:02.966
ikh gedenk nit dem tog ober m'hot undz avekgefirt.

00:29:02.966 --> 00:29:05.032
dos iz shoyn geven in

00:29:05.032 --> 00:29:07.196
s'iz shoyn geven varem.
